{"tid":1542262,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"永遠不要止步，只有我們這代可以打垮中共","createTime":"2019-09-04T20:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:09:59.000Z","uid":122054,"like":114,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"734258db25aa779e7f9a38484465d65de9d6403b","tid":1542262,"uid":122054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T20:14:17.000Z","msg":"相信大家都嚮今次運動(革命)當中見到final boss係中共<br />\n一日唔打低呢個final boss<br />\n轉頭第二日就搞鳩返你<br />\n<br />\n我地香港人係對抗共產黨既最強民族<br />\n一定唔可以退縮<br />\n否則下次必比新疆更慘<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n但打完呢場仗<br />\n就要繼續推翻中共<br />\n否則中共禍害延燒全世界<br />\n香港既安定亦只會曇花一現<br />\n<br />\n對住新世代毛澤東<br />\n我地要做既係<br />\n永不放棄！<br />\n奮鬥到底！"},{"pid":"89c9648c5c094da6bd5cce791887b1a78c4b0517","tid":1542262,"uid":41545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:42:04.000Z","msg":"呢個理念正確 但唔好咁驕傲住<br />\n討論定都係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06ed4d3fb0015001ef45df860d8d4164ce4b312","tid":1542262,"uid":36113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:43:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0936f141a33be2875f98599f622c58e6816e32c1","tid":1542262,"uid":233929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:45:27.000Z","msg":"態度正確"},{"pid":"5385bbd8ef6484aab9b565ac69ad4039db303ed9","tid":1542262,"uid":41545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:46:15.000Z","msg":"共匪70大壽前絕對唔能夠停<br />\n一停我地返唔到去呢到"},{"pid":"3222b58eb9509006677eebfdf526465179e104ac","tid":1542262,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:48:00.000Z","msg":"無撚有錯"},{"pid":"85c7a4c3d9b30bfdf1f05213622b5c15068e4a3a","tid":1542262,"uid":282455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:51:48.000Z","msg":"八十後表示非常感謝"},{"pid":"5a4dda04abddb65b558f67d26b39a70b186a0499","tid":1542262,"uid":233258,"like":0,"d